content.rendered:
Directed by Ajay Bhupathi.

Written by Tajuddin Syed.

Cast Kartikeya Gummakonda(Shiva (as Karthikeya Gummakonda)). Payal Rajput(Indu). Ramki(Daddy).Rao Ramesh. Karan(Nalli). Laxman Meesala(Laxman). Dayanand Reddy(Sub Inspector (as Dayananda Reddy)). Parvathi(Indu’s Mother). Sathyasreenivas Rao(Vempa Kasi). Tenali Shakuntala(Indu’s Grandmother). Seshu(Theater Guy) .Ramesh Adithya.Bunny.Chinababu.Chowdary. Fahad Dayee(Sahil Faiz (as Sohag Hossain)).Md Ariful Islam.Krishvan.Mohan. Divya Narni(Vasanthawada Saroja’s Daughter).Rajasekhar.Ramakrishna.Saikumar. Samiran Singh(Singer).Sreenivas.Swarnakanth

Language Telugu.

Producers Dibyendu Roy Chowdhury. Aneesh Dev. Ashok Reddy Gummakonda.

Production Karthikeya Creative Works. Mango Music.
